name: Dimnet
tag_list: web-services, consulting, design, e-mail-marketing, marketing-online, outsourcing
overview:
Dimnet specializes in providing dynamic and professional web design and coding services, ranging from complex work for Fortune 500 companies, web agencies and studios, to basic projects for small businesses. Since our inception, we have worked with a wide-range of clients in maximizing their web presence through our expertise in design and knowledge.

Our services range from consultation and creation to implementation of digital solution for successful business development. We design exclusive websites for large institutions, provide basic programming for small enterprises and help marketers achieve the greatest efficiencies.
